If someone finds these, let the list know!  I need them too!

> Also, how does one remove the rear view mirror from a 71 bus?

At the base of the arm you will find two wrench flats on the lock ring.
Loosen the ring counterclockwise and then unscrew the mirror from its
socket in the door by spinning it round and round.

George Lyle
